## Limitations

This report is based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives or the latest research developments in the field of immunology and public health. Additionally, the effectiveness of herd immunity can vary depending on the disease and the specific population dynamics. Further research and data are necessary to fully understand the long-term impacts of vaccination on community health.

